sellerCard.description:
I'm Jannatul, an aspiring Web Developer with a broad range of both professional and personal technical achievements.

5+ years of web development experience, with the past four years spent honing skills with WordPress, Wix, Squarespace, Shopify, Webflow, GoDaddy, Kajabi, and other CMS website development.

I understand the importance of excellent communication and pride myself on producing modern and professional websites.

description.content:
Tired of GENERIC websites? Looking for an expert developer to design a lovely, functional website that brings a "wow" feeling using Webflow or Framer?


Cheers! You are in the right place.


With my extensive experience in website development, Framer, and Webflow website design, I have a superb blend of creativity and technical skills to create visually appealing sites that are responsive, SEO-friendly, and speed-optimized with attractive animations and interactions.


Also, I will help to convert your Figma designs into interactive experiences. Whether you're creating a personal portfolio, a business site, or an eCommerce platform, I am here to help.


Service I Offer:


  • Professional Webflow/Framer Webslte
  • Redesign Existing Websites
  • Attractive Animations & Interactions
  • Convert Figma to Webflow/Framer
  • Beautiful Color Combination
  • CMS Pages
  • Ecommerce Functionality
  • Fully Responsive Design
  • Pixel-perfect Design Implementation
  • SEO Optimization
  • Increase Performance


Why Me?


  • On-time Delivery
  • 24/7 Availability
  • Quick Response
  • Ongoing Support


Want to boost your online presence to another level? Just reach out to me today, and lets start this exciting journey together!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you convert Figma, XD and sketch design into Webflow?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can convert Figma, XD and sketch design into Webflow.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will the website be responsive across all devices?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, the website will be complete, responsive and Mobile Friendly for every kind of device.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I be able to edit my website at any time?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you can easily change anything on your website, but you don't have to do it. Just tell me I will do it.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How many revisions will I get?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will give you unlimited revisions until you get satisfied.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if I need additional features on my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I can help you add various features, such as blogging tools, galleries, contact forms, social media integration, and e-commerce capabilities. Just let me know your requirements!
